Embedder RAG - Installation Guide
==================================

Quick Start:
1. Run "start.bat" or "start.sh" to generate settings.json
2. Run "install-service.bat" to install as Windows service (optional)
3. Access API at http://localhost:8081/api/health
4. Edit generated settings.json to set directories and files for scanning.

Manual Start:
- Run "start.bat" to start in console mode

Service Management:
- Install: install-service.bat or install-service.sh
- Uninstall: uninstall-service.bat or uninstall-service.sh
- Status: nssm status EmbedderCoreRAG (Windows)
- Status: systemctl status embedder-rag-core

Logs Location:
- configurable in settings.json

Configuration:
- Edit settings.json manually, or
- Re-run config-wizard.bat

Troubleshooting:
- Check logs for errors
- Ensure port 8081 is not in use
- Run rag_embedder_service executable directly to see console output
